 languages considered include English, German and Hebrew.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jul 2019) 4aATB Movement. 4aATB-Bewegung. 4aCriterial Freezing. 4aDependenzgrammatik. 4aLong-distance Dependencies. 4aNested Dependencies. 70(DE-601)1043771430(DE-588)4058125-1aStruktur2gnd 70(DE-601)1061459240(DE-588)4058779-4aSyntax2gnd 70(DE-601)1061547450(DE-588)4056449-6aSprache2gnd 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / Syntax.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE ENGLISH 2017z978311062526408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2017z9783110547887oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831105201870 cprintz978311052012540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110522518423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110522518.jpg  a978-3-11-062526-4  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE ENGLISH 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aPDA7ENG  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSPb2017